As a seller, I want to view my store, so that I can check how it appears to customers.

As a seller, I want to see the orders I received, so that I can process and fulfill them efficiently.

As a seller, I want to see my store analytics, so that I can track performance and make data-driven decisions.

As a seller, I want to deregister my store, so that I can exit the platform when I no longer wish to sell.

As a seller, I want to see my top-selling product, so that I can focus on inventory and marketing strategies.

As a buyer, I want to click the checkout button.

As a buyer, I want to pay for my cart.

As a buyer, I want to delete my account.
